snippet.title: Angeline Era - Official Trailer | Game Devs of Color Expo 2024
snippet.description: Angeline Era is a fast-paced 3D Action-Adventure game filled with intense boss fights! Venture forth into an esoteric land of Angels and Fae, as you slash and shoot through ancient and futuristic dungeons filled with outrageous hazards, charming creatures, and unholy abominations. Check out the latest trailer for Angeline Era to see gameplay and more. Angelina Era will be available on PC, and a demo is out now on Steam.
